---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import WhatsAppButton from '../components/WhatsAppButton.astro';
---

<Layout title="Siva Nadi Astrology - Ancient Divine Predictions">
  <Header />
  
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">
          Siva Nadi Astrology
        </h1>
        
        <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Siva Nadi is one of the most powerful forms of Nadi Astrology, containing predictions written by Lord Shiva himself through enlightened sages. This divine form of astrology provides deep insights into an individual's karma, dharma, and life purpose.
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-secondary/20 rounded-lg p-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">What is Siva Nadi?</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Siva Nadi refers to the palm leaf manuscripts that contain predictions directly channeled from Lord Shiva. These sacred texts are considered especially powerful as they address not just worldly matters but also spiritual evolution and moksha (liberation).
            </p>
            <p>
              The readings from Siva Nadi often include profound spiritual guidance, details about past lives, karmic debts, and the path to spiritual enlightenment alongside practical life predictions.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">Key Features of Siva Nadi</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary text-2xl mr-3">•</span>
                <span>Divine predictions from Lord Shiva</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary text-2xl mr-3">•</span>
                <span>Deep spiritual insights and guidance</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary text-2xl mr-3">•</span>
                <span>Past life karma and its effects</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary text-2xl mr-3">•</span>
                <span>Path to spiritual liberation (moksha)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary text-2xl mr-3">•</span>
                <span>Powerful remedies for karmic issues</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary text-2xl mr-3">•</span>
                <span>Life purpose and dharma guidance</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-6 py-4 bg-primary/5">
            <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
              "Siva Nadi readings transform lives by revealing the deeper spiritual purpose behind life events."
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">- Guruji Thillaimani</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center mt-12">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-secondary transition-colors mr-4">
            Book Siva Nadi Reading
          </a>
          <a href="tel:+919500639334" class="inline-block border-2 border-primary text-primary px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Call Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
  <WhatsAppButton />
</Layout>
